data.title: Standard Front B Main Arc Rose Execute
data.description: When executing the B Site, use this Arc Rose lineup to flash Defenders holding the front of B Main. This also gets any Defender playing the boost spot to the left of main.

data.title: Standard Front A Site Execute Arc Rose
data.description: When executing the A Site, use this Arc Rose lineup to flash Defenders holding the entrance from site.

data.title: A Site Execute Razorvine for Heaven
data.description: When executing the A Site, use this Razorvine lineup to pressure Defenders looking to aggressively peek from Heaven. This will also clear anyone sitting at Flower.

data.title: Simple Mail Razorvine Clear
data.description: Clear Defenders playing towards Mail with this easy lineup.
